 The Weeknd 的新音乐可能会在本周晚些时候发布https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-music-from-the-weeknd-may-be-arriving-later-this-week-3790066?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=new-music-from-本周晚些时候可能到达的周末Liberty DunworthTue, 03 Sep 2024 09:59:04 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopR&B https://www.nme.com/?p=3790066 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-weeknd@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="作为“After Hours Til Dawn”巡演的一部分，The Weekend 在音乐会期间进行表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-weeknd@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-weeknd@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-weeknd@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-weeknd@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-weeknd@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-weeknd@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们在黎明时骑行”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-music-from-the-weeknd-may-be-arriving-later-this-week-3790066">《The Weeknd 的新音乐可能会在本周晚些时候抵达》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-weeknd@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="作为“After Hours Til Dawn”巡演的一部分，The Weekend 在音乐会期间进行表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-weeknd@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-weeknd@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-weeknd@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-weeknd@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-weeknd@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-weeknd@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weeknd">The Weeknd</a>在网上分享了一个新的预告片，暗示新音乐可能会在本周晚些时候发布。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463">《The Weeknd》——“黎明 FM”评论：深情的明星带着希望和后见之明迎接新的一天</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位真名阿贝尔·特斯法耶 (Abel Tesfaye) 的歌手近几个月来一直在向歌迷们传达新音乐的希望，这表明他正在进行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-after-hours-review-his-most-all-encompassing-record-to-date-is-also-an-existential-quandary-2632591">“After Hours”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463">“Dawn FM”</a>三部曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-teases-return-with-after-hours-and-dawn-fm-sequel-3567220">即将推出的第三章</a>可能比我们想象的更接近。</p><p>现在，他再次引发了人们的猜测——分享了他的《Blinding Lights》音乐视频中的一张动图，并附上了神秘的标题：“星期六我们在黎明时骑行”。</p><p>值得注意的是，本周六（9 月 7 日）他将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-to-play-one-night-only-show-in-brazil-with-never-before-seen-production-3775945">在圣保罗的 Estádio MorumBIS 场地进行一场一次性演出</a>，因此该帖子可能只是对此的认可。</p><p>话虽这么说，上个月这位艺术家确实再次宣传了这场演出，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-to-livestream-his-one-night-only-sao-paulo-concert-3785870">确认他将为国际粉丝直播并分享一首新歌的片段</a>。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">星期六我们在黎明骑行<a href="https://t.co/jpPwKpTJGT">pic.twitter.com/jpPwKpTJGT</a></p><p> — Abel Tesfaye (@theweeknd) <a href="https://twitter.com/theweeknd/status/1830673727131931095?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 9 月 2 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>这张 Instagram 预告片只是 The Weeknd 分享的与他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-teases-return-with-after-hours-and-dawn-fm-sequel-3567220">即将推出的三部曲第三章</a>有关的少数预告片之一。 7月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-shares-snippet-of-new-music-in-cinematic-teaser-3777326">，他在社交媒体上分享了一段看似新歌的片段</a>，并附有电影预告片和神秘的标题，引用了德国哲学家弗里德里希·尼采的话：“当你凝视深渊足够长的时间时，深渊也在凝视着你...... ”</p><p>然后，8 月 6 日，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-previews-more-new-music-with-dark-teaser-video-3781291">通过一段包含两首新歌的黑暗预告片</a>分享了另一种新音乐品味。与恐怖主题相呼应，第二首歌似乎暗示着一种不祥的力量，他唱道“你可以改变位置，你可以改变你的名字/他们总会找到办法”。</p><p>三部曲的最后一张将成为 The Weeknd 自 2022 年的《Dawn FM》以来的首张专辑。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463"><em>NME</em>在四星评论中写道</a>：“《Dawn FM》感觉像是 The Weeknd 寻找内心平静之旅的第一步；也许下次我们收到他的消息时，他就会完全拥抱光明。”</p><p>至于他即将在巴西举行的演出，布景将与他在北美、欧洲、英国和拉丁美洲进行的破纪录巡演不同，而是专注于推出新的表演。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-to-play-one-night-only-show-in-brazil-with-never-before-seen-production-3775945">预计这将包括之前演出的混合曲目和“前所未见的制作”</a> 。</p><p>其他新闻方面，今年早些时候有报道称，The Weeknd 的热门单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknds-blinding-lights-becomes-first-song-ever-to-hit-four-billion-streams-on-spotify-3570777">《Blinding Lights》成为 Spotify 历史上第一首达到 40 亿次播放量的歌曲</a>。这首歌曲被评为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknds-blinding-lights-becomes-spotifys-most-streamed-song-of-all-time-3372843">Spotify 有史以来播放量最多的歌曲</a>，收录在他于 2019 年底发行的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-after-hours-review-his-most-all-encompassing-record-to-date-is-also-an-existential-quandary-2632591">《After Hours》</a>中。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-music-from-the-weeknd-may-be-arriving-later-this-week-3790066">《The Weeknd 的新音乐可能会在本周晚些时候抵达》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
